  "content_text": "Holo火龙果的专属运算设备在Indiegogo上众筹已近3个月\n早在第一个月就已达成众筹最低目标\n随着Holo火龙果热度增加\n设备也被不断售出\n目前共计售出1851台\n（其中HoloPort 1018台，HoloPort Nano 491台，HoloPort+342台）\n目前Indiegogo上剩余设备已不多\n目前暂未收到官方增售的消息\nHoloPort Nano剩余59台\nHoloPort剩余13台\nHoloPort+剩余11台\n根据Holo开发路线图\nHolochain Alpha版将率先对Indiegogo上的支持者开放",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"news_detail\">\n<p>Holo火龙果的专属运算设备在Indiegogo上众筹已近3个月</p><p>早在第一个月就已达成众筹最低目标</p><p>随着Holo火龙果热度增加</p><p>设备也被不断售出</p><p>目前共计售出1851台</p><p>（其中HoloPort 1018台，HoloPort Nano 491台，HoloPort+342台）</p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"400\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-width=\"600\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414913928.webp\"/></p><p>目前Indiegogo上剩余设备已不多</p><p>目前暂未收到官方增售的消息</p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"1510\" data-ratio=\"2.323077\" data-width=\"650\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414505583.webp\"/></p><p>HoloPort Nano剩余59台</p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"1514\" data-ratio=\"2.300912\" data-width=\"658\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414583261.webp\"/></p><p>HoloPort剩余13台</p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"1442\" data-ratio=\"2.204893\" data-width=\"654\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414650440.webp\"/></p><p>HoloPort+剩余11台</p><p><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"845\" data-ratio=\"1.215827\" data-width=\"695\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414177411.webp\"/></p><p>根据Holo开发路线图</p><p>Holochain Alpha版将率先对Indiegogo上的支持者开放</p><p><img class=\"\" data-height=\"410\" data-ratio=\"0.37963\" data-width=\"1080\" src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20191023011104im_/https://file-cdn.tuoniaox.com/d/file/custom/200739/image/201812/1544603414239859.webp\"/></p><p><br/></p> </div>",
